parameters:
Innkeeper: Next up, we have a newcomer! A girl with the face
of a child but the body of an adult... It's Clea-chan!

Clea (The man with the knife tattoo... Can I find him among
this crowd?)

Enthusiastic Spectator: W-Why does that girl have a
greatsword?

Drunk Spectator: I-I don't understand... Is she a spy for
the Imperial Army?
Experienced Spectator: Oh, Foti Zona Style, huh...

Experienced Spectator: It is said that the prototype of pole
dancing, which has now become common, was a dance for
comfort on the battlefield.

Experienced Spectator: Ormos, the genius dancer... It is
said that she would thrust her greatsword into the ground
and dance around it as the axis.

Experienced Spectator: I never thought I would be able to
see the successor while still alive.
Clea (Let's set the greatsword aside for now)

Enthusiastic Spectator: H-Hey, she just casually set it
aside, right?

Experienced Spectator: I see... So she came from that
direction.
Drunk Spectator: Which way is 'that direction'?

Clea (I don't really understand, but for now, let's try to
do movements that look like it)

Clea (But it's darker than I expected... It's difficult to
find someone with a tattoo here.)

Man with a knife tattoo: G-Get out of the way! I came here
for some long-awaited fun!

Man with a knife tattoo: Hey, look over here! Give me more
service, please!

Man with a knife tattoo: Oh, you saw me! Nice, it's great,
I'm glad to be alive!
Man with a knife tattoo: Oh, you came over here!
Clea: I won't let the man with the knife tattoo escape!

Man with a knife tattoo: Huh... Could it be... the
organization!?

Innkeeper: Next up is the newcomer... huh, is this girl? Are
you sure she'll be okay... um, this is the genius Relm-
chan!
Mage Relm (Why do I have to do something like this...)

Mage Relm (Should I act like a dancer and quickly find the
man and leave? Otherwise, my intelligence might decrease.)

Drunk spectator: Maybe she was sold around the campus...
that's kind of pitiful... well, maybe not.
Experienced spectator: I don't get excited by small breasts.

Man with a knife tattoo: I sense potential, but... it might
have been too early for her to step on the stage.

Mage Relm: I can hear everything, you know! Don't make fun
of me...!
Mage Relm: You've made me angry...!

Man with a knife tattoo: It's dazzling...! What is this,
magic...!?
Mage Relm: Huh... a knife tattoo!

Mage Relm: This is lucky! I've found a legitimate reason to
attack!

Man with a knife tattoo: Huh... Could it be... the
organization!?
Mage Relm: I won't let you escape, no matter what!

Innkeeper: Next up is the debut of a newcomer! With a big
body and a girl's heart... it's Nora-chan!

Thief Nora (Ugh, there are so many men... They're looking at
me with such intense eyes... It's scary...)

Thief Nora (There are so many people... I wonder if I'll be
able to find him in this crowd...)

Drunk spectator: How long are you going to space out for?!
Start stripping already!

Thief Nora: Ah, s-sorry! I'll start, so please don't get
angry, okay?
Thief Nora: I-Is this... okay like this?

Enthusiastic spectator: Give us more service! We paid a lot
of money to come here, you know!
Thief Nora: Ah, ahh! I'm sorry!

Thief Nora (Ugh, it's scary, I don't want to, I want to go
home...)

Man with a knife tattoo: Don't blame her, you guys! It's
obvious that a newcomer would shrink back if they were
showered with abuse!

Man with a knife tattoo: I didn't come here to see scared
women, I came to see the art of strip dancing.

Man with a knife tattoo: Come on, you don't have to be
scared. It's okay.
Thief Nora: Ah... a knife tattoo.
Thief Nora: I've been looking for you! Now, come with me!

Man with a knife tattoo: Huh... Could it be... the
organization!?

Thief Nora: Wait... Ah, I don't have a weapon...! That's
right, I'm sorry, may I borrow your pole!

Bar Manager: Introducing a super rookie...! It's the
beautiful Sophia who will rewrite the history of the stage!
I am Sophia the priestess. Please treat me kindly.

Priestess Sophia (Shall we search while dancing... It would
be great if we can find it quickly)

Drunk audience member: Get out of the way, you guys! Let us
get closer to the stage!

Enthusiastic audience member: Shut up! We won't give up this
spot no matter what!

Experienced Audience Member: The commotion caused by these
men... It's not just charming... It's truly bewitching!

Man with a knife tattoo: Don't push me while muttering
something like that!

Man with a knife tattoo: This is the strip club I came to
during my life on the run! Sophia-san is the blessing given
to us by the goddess Delia!

Priestess Sophia: Oh... a knife tattoo... Hehe, it's so
manly and wonderful, isn't it?
Man with a knife tattoo: Ehehe... Do you think so?

Priestess Sophia: Oh my... Someone touched my body towards
the person with the knife tattoo!

Priestess Sophia: Sniff... I'm too scared to dance
anymore...

Man with a knife tattoo: H-Hey, what are you saying...!
Don't look at me like that...!

Priestess Sophia: Oh, they ran away. I'm worried if I can
catch them by myself.
Man with a knife tattoo: Ugh... ugh...
Clea: I apologize for causing you all trouble.

Expert Audience: Using a greatsword as a weapon... This is a
paradigm shift in strip dancing!

Drunk audience member: No, that's just the normal way to use
it.
Man with a knife tattoo: Ugh... ugh...

Mage Relm: With this, our objective is achieved. Do any of
you have anything to say to me?
Audience: It was an amazing stage!
Mage Relm: Very well...! Then please help me carry the man.
Man with a knife tattoo: Ugh... ugh...

Thief Nora: I'm glad... I can go home now... U-um, sorry for
the trouble, I'll take my leave!
Enthusiastic audience member: He tore the pole apart!

Drunk audience member: I've sobered up... There's no way we
can win against them.
Man with a knife tattoo: Ugh... ugh...

Priestess Sophia: Everyone, thank you so much for your help.
We will be leaving for today...

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, let's meet on the stage someday,
shall we?
